displayName: Emma Thief Gang Hideout, Captain Clevo's Room

parameters: Captain Clevo: I'll leave it to Nora.

Captain Clevo: You are expelled... Please leave before you
get involved in the conflict.
Captain Clevo: You're back. Did you bring back any harvest?
Thief Nora: Captain! Captain! Captain Clevo~!
Thief Nora: I found it~! Look, these are dragon eyes!

Thief Nora: Captain, didn't you mention it before?! If we
have treasures as valuable as dragon eyes, everyone will be
saved!

Captain Clevo: Dragon eyes... for something like that...
you...

Captain Clevo: I thought for sure you had been captured by
the nobles. I'm really glad you're safe... You had me
worried...!
Thief Nora: Ehehe... I'm sorry, Captain.

Priestess Sophia: I heard you're the leader of the thief
gang, but you give off more of a fatherly vibe, don't you?

Mage Relm: It's good that we could meet again! Well, if we
give it our all, this should be a piece of cake.

Captain Clevo: I'm Captain Clevo, the leader of the Emma
Thief Gang. I appreciate you safely rescuing my comrade,
Nora.

Clea: I haven't protected her. We traveled together and
fought dragons together as comrades.

Thief Nora: These dragon eyes are the real deal! I took them
from the dragons we defeated!
Captain Clevo: So the rumors about dragon slaying were true.
Captain Clevo: I've met a good comrade, Nora.

Thief Nora: Yes! They are just as important to me as my
fellow members of the thief gang!

Captain Clevo: Do you have any information regarding the
Empire Army of Camps?

Experienced Emma Thief Gang Member: No... nothing in
particular.
Captain Clevo: You really don't have any information?

Captain Clevo: Our young ones attacked the Empire Army's
transportation route.

Captain Clevo: If there's no information, it means the
attack failed and everyone in the Empire Army was killed...

Captain Clevo: It means that for the Empire Army, it was an
insignificant event not even worth reporting.

Captain Clevo: Nora, as of today, you are expelled from the
Emma Thief Gang.

Thief Nora: W-Why!? I mean, I did leave on my own accord,
but why!

Thief Nora: I have the Dragon's Eye! I even got permission
from the Queen herself, so--

Captain Clevo: It's no longer a matter of that dimension.
The noble Pido's objective is clear... our annihilation.

Thief Nora: Then let's leave this place together! We can all
live together in a safe place, isn't that a good idea?

Thief Nora: We traveled all over the Empire with Clea-san
and the others! There are plenty of good places, even better
than here--

Captain Clevo: We had our comrades taken away in the war,
and when we returned from the war, the nobles had taken away
our land.

Captain Clevo: And we, who had our comrades taken away once
again, will not retreat. We cannot retreat.
Captain Clevo: Can I rely on Nora? I want her to be happy.

Clea: I understand. However, I don't think Nora will give up
on all of you.
